Mercedes-Benz Club of Kenya hosted a Horse Power event in partnership with Nairobi Polo Club on March 7. The event aimed to showcase equestrianism performance and automotive prowess by merging majestic horses and unmatched Mercedes-Benz cars. MBCK was formed by a group of Benz owners for better understanding of their cars and for technical support from each other. The event also helps people to network and have fun through music and different activities.